headline: United Rentals (URI) Raises Full-Year Outlook on Strong Rental Growth and Fleet Productivity
summary: United Rentals, Inc. (NYSE:URI) ranks among the stocks to benefit from an onshoring boom. After strong second-quarter performance, United Rentals, Inc. (NYSE:URI) increased its full-year 2025 outlook for total revenue, adjusted EBITDA, net cash from operations, and free cash flow on July 23. The company reported a revenue of $3.94 billion, with rental revenue rising […]
